Why?
Oxford Street Revealed
-
Series 2 Reversions: Episode 7
Observational documentary series. Oxford Street comes to a standstill as protesting cabbies take their grievances to the street.
Oxford Street comes to a standstill as protesting cabbies take their grievances to the street. The police and transport control try to keep the street, and its buses, moving. Cosmetic chain Lush prepare for the opening of their biggest ever store, with a little help from a rock superstar.
